icle smoothing is a useful\nadjunct to already highly resolved simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Jan 2015 21:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2015 07:33:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
