 examples are considered and\nwe find in all cases a very good agreement between the analytical and numerical\nresults.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Jan 2015 13:29:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 1 Feb 2015 10:51:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-03"}
