ve signals, and when performing parameter\nestimation in the event of a detection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Jan 2015 15:32:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jul 2015 10:33:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-19"}
